snippet.title: Nick DiRamio
snippet.description:
Hi! I'm Nick DiRamio! (He/They) I created my series Clip Breakdown so we can dive into the latest movies, TV, and trending videos and look at them clip by clip. I love using my background in film and production and my love of sarcasm and sass to create funny video essays that analyze new movies, nostalgic movies, Disney Channel Originals, Lifetime movies, YouTuber content, low budget music videos, and more!

SUBSCRIBE: http://bit.ly/2d39mcU

Subscribe to my channel (http://bit.ly/2d39mcU) to get updated with my weekly videos! Thank you to all who are already subscribed for being a part of the Nick D Crew. 💕

Visit my site for blog articles: https://www.nickdiramio.com/

MAILING ADDRESS
Nick DiRamio
5419 Hollywood Blvd Ste C - #430
Hollywood, CA 90027 USA
